latestIgtvVideos.title: Favorite VAPOUR BEAUTY Products
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Presenting some of my favorite @vapourbeauty products! Their Luminous Foundation is exactly that - luminous. It gives my skin such a beautiful healthy glow and it is 100% waterless! I’m using shade 115L. The Bronzing Stick in Simmer blends so easily and leaves the perfect natural shimmer to the skin. I’m also loving their Aura Multi Stick in Spark - it leaves such a beautiful natural flush to the cheeks! And their Highlight Stick in Moonlight will give you the perfect dewy glow. I love finishing everything off with their Perfecting Powder Pressed and some Lux Conditioning Tint in Hush on my lips. And voila! The most natural, effortless, glowy look achieved! Use code michelewang20 on the @vapourbeauty site to get 20% off your order! •#VapourBeauty #VapourBeautyPartner #RevealYourself #BeWildlyUnique @nordstrombeauty #ad

Meet the NEW @givenchybeauty Le Rouge Sheer Velvet Lipstick! It is a sheer matte lipstick that has buildable lip color with a blurred, soft-focus effect. I tried both the @givenchybeauty Le Rouge Deep Velvet and Sheer Velvet Matte lipsticks in shades 10, 27, 36, and 37. Loved them all! It’s available in 10 shades, which are coordinated with the Le Rouge Deep Velvet Lipstick shades! For a sheer, blurred matte finish, try the new Sheer Velvet. And for a highly-pigmented matte finish, try the Deep Velvet formula. Both are housed in refillable, velvet, luxuriously chic cases. Which shade and finish do you want to try? PS - I hear shade 10 is selling fast and 16 is also an amazing nude shade! Shop link in my profile ❤️
